a little bit of cleaning up in here.

11:46.921 --> 11:49.633
Yeah, yeah.
I'll get to that one later.

11:51.510 --> 11:53.136
That's our stall.

11:54.679 --> 11:56.014
Yeah, I'm aware.

11:56.097 --> 11:57.974
I'm married now.

11:58.057 --> 11:59.393
I took vows.

11:59.476 --> 12:01.102
You know, it's, uh...

12:01.185 --> 12:03.938
it's not cheating
if you're in different zip codes, right?

12:05.231 --> 12:08.234
And, uh, there's no dick.

12:08.318 --> 12:10.487
So... that's a freebie.

12:10.570 --> 12:15.241
It's cheating if I even
think about somebody else.

12:15.325 --> 12:19.120
Lusting in the heart and all that?
Just like Jimmy Carter says.

12:26.336 --> 12:28.463
