you didn't miss me at all?

12:29.798 --> 12:31.383
[whispering] You didn't think about me?

12:32.926 --> 12:34.553
'Cause I sure missed you.

12:37.347 --> 12:38.848
Of course I missed you...

12:40.434 --> 12:43.102
but that was because
I was worried about you.

12:44.521 --> 12:46.189
[man speaking indistinctly on PA]

12:47.732 --> 12:49.401
Look.

12:49.484 --> 12:53.655
Look, there's the little chip in the tile
from when you cut your arm.

12:53.738 --> 12:56.950
Aw, remember you didn't notice
until after your third orgasm?

12:57.033 --> 12:59.869
Okay, no.
No, you are not helping me.

12:59.953 --> 13:02.706
You're making me think about things
I should not be thinking about.

13:02.789 --> 13:05.417
It's not right, Nicky. [sighs]

13:08.169 --> 13:09.504
Where'd you go?

13:14.676 --> 13:16.928
No, stay there. Don't!

13:17.011 --> 13:18.805
[groaning] Leave me alone.

13:18.888 --> 13:20.932
Baby, I'm here.

13:21.933 --> 13:26.020
I can touch you.
You need to be touched.

13:27.313 --> 13:28.898
He can't give that to you.

13:30.108 --> 13:32.611
Uh, no.
No, no, no, no, no, no.

13:32.694 --> 13:34.363
Okay, no!

13:34.446 --> 13:36.823
Vinny and I,
we have a future.

13:36.906 --> 13:38.450
Sure.

13:38.533 --> 13:39.701
Or you have no future

13:39.784 --> 13:42.496
'cause you're virtual strangers
living in a fantasy world.

13:43.747 --> 13:45.832
And it's gonna shatter
into a million pieces

13:45.915 --> 13:48.877
when the mundane realities
of day-to-day life

13:48.960 --> 13:53.339
intrude on your maiden-in-a-tower,
prince-down-below fairy-tale bullshit.

13:54.424 --> 13:55.634
'Cause it's retarded.

13:55.717 --> 13:58.720
Plus he's probably been banging the single
mom next door the whole time, anyway,

13:58.803 --> 14:01.390
because who can live on fantasy
and promises for that long, right?

14:01.473 --> 14:03.475
People get lonely.

14:06.645 --> 14:08.730
Or not.
Okay?

14:10.690 --> 14:12.233
Maybe it's the real thing.

14:13.317 --> 14:15.737
I've never met the guy.

14:15.820 --> 14:17.947
For all I know,
maybe it's true love, right?

14:18.698 --> 14:21.743
Are you sure he wouldn't get off
on hearing about you with another chick?

14:23.620 --> 14:25.622
[Piscatella] Owens!
[Owens] Here.

14:25.705 --> 14:27.749
[Piscatella] Piendak!
[Piendak] Here.

14:27.832 --> 14:29.543
[Piscatella] Sankey!
[Sankey] Here.

14:29.626 --> 14:30.710
[Piscatella] Watson!

14:31.795 --> 14:34.255
Let me hear
a verbal confirmation, inmate.

14:34.338 --> 14:35.382
[softly] Here.

14:35.465 --> 14:36.758
A little bit louder now!

14:36.841 --> 14:38.217
-[shouts] Here!
-Ow!

14:38.301 --> 14:39.678
-What?
-Nothing, sorry.

14:39.761 --> 14:41.680
My ear was too close to your mouth.
My bad.

14:41.763 --> 14:46.476
Now, ladies, due to the breach in security
at the Whispers factory,

14:46.560 --> 14:49.771
it has been decided
that all employees of Whispers

14:49.854 --> 14:52.315
will be replaced
with more trustworthy inmates.

14:52.399 --> 14:54.067
